products.product_name: VIP Energy Satin Scarf Halter Maxi Dress Black
products.description: Length from bust to hem of size S: 144cm. Chest: 38cm, Waist: 35cm, size S. Maxi dress. Lined. Model is a standard XS and is wearing size XS. Stretch. Satin. Halter. Cowl neckline. Zipper, hook eye closure. Cold hand wash. Polyester/Spandex. Please Note: This dress is exclusive to Dear Emilia. The VIP Energy Satin Scarf Halter Maxi Dress is made for spotlight moments. Featuring luxe satin, a halter fit, and a draped cowl neckline, this gown exudes elegance with every step. Pair it with strappy stilettos and a sleek clutch for evening allure, or add statement earrings to make the neckline the star.
